msgctxt "Description"
msgid ""
"Highlight areas of the desktop that have been recently updated; activated "
"with a keyboard shortcut"
msgstr ""
"Nabarmendu berriki eguneratu diren mahaigaineko eremuak; teklatuko "
"lasterbide batekin aktibatua"

